title: Bobby’s Top 5 Hated Bands + Fun Fact Friday Faceoff: Eddie vs. Morgan2 + Justin Moore Performs His First Ever Hit!
itunes:title: Bobby’s Top 5 Hated Bands + Fun Fact Friday Faceoff: Eddie vs. Morgan2 + Justin Moore Performs His First Ever Hit!
description:
Bobby gives his list of 5 artists that he thinks get the most undeserving hate. We weigh in on if it’s justified or not. Eddie and Morgan2 battle it out to see who has the 5 most fun facts of the week. Justin Moore drops in to talk about his new album and perform his first no. 1!
